Template: conscia-node/components
Type: multiselect
Choices: ConSoul (Desktop Admin Console), Zrok (Public HTTPS Tunnel)
Default: ConSoul (Desktop Admin Console)
_Description: Select optional components to install:
 The Conscia daemon is the core lifeline and is always installed.
 ConSoul is the desktop management interface.
 Zrok provides public HTTPS URLs (optional, not required for P2P mesh).

Template: conscia-node/mesh_namespace
Type: string
Default: sovereign_mesh
_Description: Mesh network namespace:
 Enter a human-readable identifier for your mesh network.

Template: conscia-node/api_port
Type: string
Default: 3000
_Description: Conscia API port:
 The port for the HTTP/WebSocket interface (includes signaling relay).
